    {
      "id": "bootstrap-tutorial-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Start Here",
      "position": {
        "x": 760,
        "y": -460
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bootstrap Tutorial\n\nThis tutorial no longer embeds the old bootstrap node.\n\nInstead:\n\n1. Open the onboarding guide\n2. Use the toolbar onboarding button to copy the LLM handoff\n3. Paste that handoff into your chatbot\n4. Paste the chatbot's JSON transaction back into Twilite\n5. Start from a blank graph once the handshake succeeds"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bootstrap-tutorial-step-1",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 1",
      "position": {
        "x": 760,
        "y": -150
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 1 — Open the onboarding guide\n\nUse the port on this graph to open the canonical onboarding guide. Read it once so you know what the chatbot is being asked to do."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bootstrap-tutorial-step-2",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 2",
      "position": {
        "x": 760,
        "y": 110
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 2 — Use the toolbar onboarding button\n\nThe toolbar copies the current onboarding handoff. Paste that handoff into your chatbot and require a JSON-only transaction response."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bootstrap-tutorial-step-3",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 3",
      "position": {
        "x": 760,
        "y": 390
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "color": "rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.14)",
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 3 — Paste the transaction and continue\n\nPaste the returned JSON transaction into Twilite. Once the handshake works, create a new file and dismiss the welcome screen to start from a blank graph."
      }
    },
